General.Name: Complex Micro Interconnection Co. Ltd.
General.Description: Complex Micro Interconnection Co.,Ltd. produces and sells electronic components in Taiwan. It offers flexible printed circuit boards and assemblies, electronic wires, electronic distribution reels, flexible and hard composite boards, wire harness, and LED car light modules. The company was founded in 1969 and is based in New Taipei City, Taiwan.
General.Address: No. 4, Lane 130, Minquan Road, New Taipei City, Taiwan, 23141
